show.title: Love Reloaded
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/8uEqQU
show.description: Raman Mahadeva, a wealthy but lonely businessman, hides his true identity in search of genuine love. Radha, a resilient food stall owner scarred by betrayal and loss, crosses his path with her strength and determination. Their bond deepens into something when Radha’s search for her daughter—lost years ago—intertwines with Raman’s world. As destiny brings them closer through Jaanu, secrets unfold, love is tested, and broken relationships find new meaning. Watch "Love Reloaded" only on KUKU TV!
